        <p>
            When you assign ratings, don't try and analyze the words;
            just assign ratings quickly based on your first impression.
            There are no right or wrong answers!
        </p>
        <p>
            The spelling for each word will also be shown to help clarify
            the sounds you hear. Some of the spellings may look a bit strange,
            so keep in mind they are only there as a guide to the sounds
            you hear.
            Try and base your judgments only on the sound of the word,
